title: Shuttle Plus Music Player v.1.5.0 Beta 8
description:
Changelog:
- New (not final) icon
- Fixed a bunch of crashes
- Fixed issue where playlist name would not stay in the action bar after collapsing and expanding the now playing view.
- Fixed theming issue of 'drag handle' in editable playlists
- Added option to crop artwork (I think this option is inverted, i.e. it does the opposite of what you choose in settings)
- Reduced the app size a little.

PLEASE READ:
- Uninstall any previous version of Shuttle before update and seed!
